Package: FFSGShinyAppP
Type: Package
Title: Provides tools including an interactable shiny app to understand fatal encounters with police
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Madeline Cummins, Martina Morris
Maintainer: Madeline Cummins <maddic9@uw.edu>
Description: A package meant to provide tools and a shiny app to 
  help users explore fatal encounters with police. Functions can be
  used on their own but it is recommended to be viewed in the shiny app.
